This agent is part of an event-driven incident response team. Emphasize their on-call responsibilities, escalation thresholds, and communication protocols.

Fields:
- soul: 3 sentences (SRE persona, incident role and thresholds, escalation style)
- agentsMd: 2 sentences (session startup: monitoring context to check, actions to take)
- userMd: 1 sentence (profile of the engineering lead or on-call manager this agent serves)
- identityMd: "Name: X | Creature: X | Vibe: X | Emoji: X"
